2011-04-11 Mon  Jari Aalto  <jari.aalto@cante.net>

        * README (Project details): Fix typo in word "generates".

        * epackage.el: (top level::The Info File): Move
        "Depends" after "Description"; keeps item in alphabetical
        order.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-header): Correct header.
        (epackage-loader-insert-file-path-list-by-path): Use
        `abbreviate-file-name'.
        (epackage-loader-file-insert-install-code): Sort list of files.
        This is important because "autoloads" must be before "install"
        and "xactivate". This fixes epackage-loader.el load problems.
        (epackage-loader-file-insert-install-code): Move point to
        the eob before exiting function.
        (epackage-sort): New.
        (epackage-pkg-info-status-warnings): Use `epackage-sort'.
        (epackage-sources-list-info-pkg-list): Use `epackage-sort'.
        (epackage-insert-file-contents): New.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-help): Adjust wording.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-prompt): New.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-actions): Add "m" for
        `epackage-batch-ui-display-menu'.
        (epackage-batch-ui-display-menu): New.
        (epackage-batch-ui-menu): Show `epackage--batch-ui-menu-prompt',
        and full menu only after "m" to reduce display.
        (epackage-batch-ui-display-version): New.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-actions): Add "v"
        Â´epackage-batch-ui-display-version'.
        (epackage-batch-ui-display-package-action-list): New.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-header): Rewrite.
        (epackage-batch-ui-download-action-enable-toggle): Call
        `epackage-batch-ui-display-package-action-list'.
        (epackage-batch-ui-download-action-activate-toggle): Call
        `epackage-batch-ui-display-package-action-list'.
        (epackage-status-installed-packages): Include 'activated'
        packages too.
        (epackage-status-not-installed-packages): Correct function.
        Use `epackage-status-installed-packages'.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-header): Display version.
        (epackage-initialize): move let `epackage--initialize-flag' a
        little earler. This prvents "make ui" error on pristine
        call where nothing has been done yet.
        (epackage-ssh-known-host-p): New.
        (epackage-ssh-config-strict-key-check-disabled-p): New.
        (epackage-auto-revert-mode-p): New.
        (epackage-turn-on-auto-revert-mode): New.
        (epackage-require-ssh): New.
        (epackage-download-sources-list): Add call to
        `epackage-require-ssh' prior downloading from gitub.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-string): Remove B command.
        (epackage--batch-ui-menu-actions): Comment out B command.
        The Byte compile is in "y" command already.
        (epackage-with-git-command): Add `abbreviate-file-name'.
        (epackage-ssh-help-string): New.
        (epackage-ssh-p): New.
        (epackage-url-extract-host): New.
        (epackage-download-sources-list): Add SSH configurrion and
        stop on error unless ok.
        (epackage-git-command-clone): Use `epackage-require-ssh'.

